  <Description>Version: 1.0.0
Net-JSON-Library-Csharp is a lightweight and efficient library designed to simplify JSON handling in C# applications. Whether you're working on web APIs, data processing pipelines, or any project requiring JSON manipulation, this library provides a robust and developer-friendly solution.

Key Features
Efficient JSON Parsing: Quickly parse JSON strings into C# objects with minimal overhead.
Seamless Serialization and Deserialization: Convert complex C# objects to JSON and vice versa with ease.
Customizable Options: Fine-tune settings such as formatting, null handling, and property naming conventions.
Error Handling: Built-in mechanisms to gracefully handle malformed JSON or unexpected data structures.
Lightweight Design: Minimal dependencies ensure fast performance and easy integration into your projects.
What's New in This Release?
Improved Performance: Optimized algorithms for faster parsing and serialization.
Enhanced Error Messages: More descriptive error messages to help debug issues quickly.
Support for .NET [Version]: Added compatibility with the latest .NET runtime versions.
New Utility Methods: Introduced helper functions for common JSON tasks (e.g., deep cloning, partial updates).
Bug Fixes: Resolved known issues related to edge cases in nested object handling and special characters.</Description>
